  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858150/extras/aeea63068ef0b5c5898da5a514038676.poster.avif?t=1761557302\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858150/extras/aeea63068ef0b5c5898da5a514038676.webm?t=1761557302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858150/extras/aeea63068ef0b5c5898da5a514038676.mp4?t=1761557302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your fleet was betrayed and your airship barely escaped destruction. Now fight your way past waves of pirates, cultists, and sky monsters. Destroy your foes, harvest wreckage, upgrade your ship, and find your way to safety.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Menagerie of Monsters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage enemies with different attack patterns and abilities. Fight massive boss monsters that require cunning and firepower to defeat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858150/extras/1ace02239884a598d7d43c22dded0a9f.poster.avif?t=1761557302\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858150/extras/1ace02239884a598d7d43c22dded0a9f.webm?t=1761557302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858150/extras/1ace02239884a598d7d43c22dded0a9f.mp4?t=1761557302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >An Array of Airships</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick the slow but powerful Battleship, the nimble Copter, or the Science Vessel with its railgun and energy shield. Build a strategy around their strengths and weaknesses. Don't feel the need to ever stop? The Megaplane will suit you. Want to build a mighty fleet? Start with the Flagship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858150/extras/9e4317a9f5db13f1bbd4eea285c657df.poster.avif?t=1761557302\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858150/extras/9e4317a9f5db13f1bbd4eea285c657df.webm?t=1761557302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858150/extras/9e4317a9f5db13f1bbd4eea285c657df.mp4?t=1761557302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Path Planning</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose where your fleet goes on its journey. Different destinations have pros and cons in terms of what enemies you fight, the rewards you get, the available upgrades, and your relationships with local factions. For example, you can befriend cultists, gaining their Worm Blessings and their aid in future battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858150/extras/c2195d0d4dc27ae1805ac4c7ec8d4800.poster.avif?t=1761557302\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858150/extras/c2195d0d4dc27ae1805ac4c7ec8d4800.webm?t=1761557302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858150/extras/c2195d0d4dc27ae1805ac4c7ec8d4800.mp4?t=1761557302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Panoply of Powerups</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip your ship with cannons, rockets, aerial torpedoes, mines, gatling guns, and more. Strengthen it with modules like ammo elevators, guard barracks, command posts. Host strange temples.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improve your ship with training for your crew, more armor plating, or senior officers. Pick a doctrine to gain its advantages: terrify your enemies, dodge incoming attacks, make your money through trade. Find powerful combinations that lay waste to your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858150/extras/66e0e983a890ca3859169c1e67e33865.poster.avif?t=1761557302\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858150/extras/66e0e983a890ca3859169c1e67e33865.webm?t=1761557302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858150/extras/66e0e983a890ca3859169c1e67e33865.mp4?t=1761557302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Charismatic Captains</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock captains for your ship that give you powerful advantages and disadvantages and change the rules of your game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858150/extras/6ecfce69d3005b4927ad8f499d55a4d5.poster.avif?t=1761557302\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858150/extras/6ecfce69d3005b4927ad8f499d55a4d5.webm?t=1761557302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858150/extras/6ecfce69d3005b4927ad8f499d55a4d5.mp4?t=1761557302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strange Stelae</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Temples and monoliths as well as more familiar ports float in the skies, changing the game rules in parts of the map. Disadvantage your enemies and boost your abilities with careful positioning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858150/extras/20359720325361abf66e8bbdd00ada61.poster.avif?t=1761557302\" width=1170 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858150/extras/20359720325361abf66e8bbdd00ada61.webm?t=1761557302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858150/extras/20359720325361abf66e8bbdd00ada61.mp4?t=1761557302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
